# Reference photos with unrecoverable provenance — kept locally for
# bake-time iteration; excluded from the public repo for rights diligence.
# NOTE: these are already tracked in earlier history; this pattern only
# prevents future re-adds. Pre-publish action is to `git rm --cached` each
# path so the next commit drops them from the index.
node/canon/reference_photos/02_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/05_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/07_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/09_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/10_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/11_*.jpg
node/canon/reference_photos/12_*.jpg

# Internal handoff/log docs not intended for public review.
# NOTE: most of these are already tracked from earlier sessions; this
# pattern only prevents future re-adds. Pre-publish action is to
# `git rm --cached <path>` for each, then commit.
docs/STATUS_FOR_BASHAR.md
